title: Christmas Bird Holiday Card w/Clip
description:
Bring a touch of personality to your stationery repertoire. This card is crafted from the finest paper featuring carefully embellished and playful motifs with a unique surprise - a golden multi-use metal clip. The clip is cleverly incorporated into the design of the card and can be used as an eye-catching bookmark, to organize papers, or simply to add a touch of style to your planner or journal.

Perfect for thank-you’s, invitations, or to simply show you care.

  • Dimensions: Card size: 4.5 x 6 in. Metal clip size: Approx. 1.8 x 1.6 in.
  • Materials: Heavyweight card w/ envelope. Galvanized stainless steel multi-use clip
  • Blank inside for your own message
